+# Trevo Vault iOS Changelog
+
+## Unreleased
+- Rename app display name and bundle identifier to Trevo Vault (`finance.trevo.vault`).
+- Replace user-facing strings and links with Trevo resources.
+- Add Trevo network icon.
+- Update privacy policy and terms of service.
+- Apply Trevo dark palette with black accents.
